    "Snapshots are shown for the phases: Z + q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM (T /J1 = 0.14), Z - q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM (T /J1 = 0.17), QLRO ⊕ Z2 NM (T /J1 = 0.23), and PM (T /J1 = 0.3).",
